  "abstract": "Based on the differential reaction of 10 chickpea cultivars to pathogenic isolates of Fusarium oxysporum f. sp. ciceri, the existence of at least four races of the fungus has been demonstrated. It is suggested that these be called races 1, 2, 3, and 4.",
